00:03:00.775 --> 00:03:02.462
Here, I have an asset,

00:03:02.462 --> 00:03:05.143
which is my equipment and the building

00:03:05.143 --> 00:03:07.933
and all of the computers
and all of the things,

00:03:07.933 --> 00:03:09.942
all of the things that can
essentially run a bank,

00:03:09.942 --> 00:03:13.491
and that's worth $10 million,

00:03:13.491 --> 00:03:15.192
and this is my owner's equity.

00:03:15.192 --> 00:03:17.492
So i have $10 million of owner's equity.

